# рџ”— URL Shortener

A full-stack MERN URL Shortener application that allows users to create short links, manage them from a personal dashboard, and track click analytics such as browser, device, operating system, IP address, and location.

## рџЊђ Live Demo

**Frontend:** https://url-shortner-mu-gold.vercel.app

**Backend API:** https://url-shortner-r2u6.onrender.com

---

## вњЁ Features

- User Authentication (JWT)
- User Registration & Login
- Create Short URLs
- Automatic Redirection
- Personal Dashboard
- Copy Short URL
- Delete Short URLs
- Click Analytics
- Browser Detection
- Operating System Detection
- Device Detection
- IP Address Tracking
- Country, Region & City Tracking
- Responsive UI
- Secure Password Hashing (bcrypt)

